In this stage, there are 2 options:
  a) You have the designer and the design, the designer wants to mess with the system. Account created.
  b) You have the design only. You have 1:1 PNG how it should look like.

Solutions:
  a) Contact frantisek.psotka@stylez.sk for account creation.
  b) Open new discussion thread in "WE WANT THIS TO COME ALIVE".

In latter case b) you should know basic concept and you have some vision of what you need. You can find
somebody who can understand this, but what is important, including me :)



